Original program:

```
ANSWER0=VQA(image=RIGHT,question='How many hyenas are in the image?')
ANSWER1=VQA(image=RIGHT,question='Are the hyenas facing left?')
ANSWER2=EVAL(expr='{ANSWER0} > 0 and {ANSWER1}')
FINAL_ANSWER=RESULT(var=ANSWER2)
```
